value.name: PartialDRBAccessibility
value.description: The Data Radio Bearer (DRB) setup success rate, including the success rate for setting up Radio Resource Control (RRC) connection and Next Generation (NG) signaling connection

value.name: DLLat_gNB_DU
value.description: The gNodeB-Distributed unit (gNB_DU) part of the packet transmission latency experienced by an end-user. It is used to evaluate the gNB latency contribution to the total packet latency

value.name: DLDelay_GnbDu
value.description: The average packet transmission delay through RAN to the UE. It is used to evaluate delay performance of NG-RAN in downlink for a network slice subnet

value.name: DlUeThroughput
value.description: The average downlink RAN UE throughput for a NRCellDU
